RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT Ssi_Mnemonic, Currency, Counterparty, Settlement_Seq_No, Customer_Name1, Product_Code, Module, Branch, Pay_Ac_Branch, Pay_Account, Pay_Account_Ccy, Recv_Ac_Branch, Recv_Account, Recv_Account_Ccy, Acc_With_Instn1, Benef_Institution1, Ult_Beneficiary1 FROM Oltms_Instr a, Oltms_Customer b WHERE a.Counterparty = ? AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND b.Customer_No = a.Counterparty AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?) ORDER BY 3, 2
SELECT CCY_CODE,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN ORDER BY 1
